      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396475,
      "updated": 1772396535
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49fcb00000000009ec62d",
      "text": "#ソシオニクス の創案者の[初期の著作]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396491,
      "updated": 1772875047
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49d6000000000009ec5fe",
      "text": "英訳：[https://wikisocion.github.io/en/index.php@title=The_Dual_Nature_of_Man.html Wikisocion] [\" This translation was done by an automatic translator.]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772395873,
      "updated": 1772397196
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49e6300000000009ec617",
      "text": "日本語訳：by [https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html From Over the Sea]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396132,
      "updated": 1772396280
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49e7400000000009ec618",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396148,
      "updated": 1772872806
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe465000000000078d47e",
      "text": "着想のもととなったもの:",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872806,
      "updated": 1772872826
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d45d",
      "text": "\t[ピョートル・ガヌシュキン]（П. Б. Ганнушкина）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d45e",
      "text": "\t[エルンスト・クレッチマー]（Kretschmer）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d45f",
      "text": "\t\t[クレッチマーの気質類型]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d460",
      "text": "\t[カール・グスタフ・ユング] (C.G. Jung)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d461",
      "text": "\tA.[ケンピンスキー]（А. Кемпинского）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d462",
      "text": "\t\t[情報代謝理論]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d463",
      "text": "\t[アンドレイ・リチコ]（А. Е. Личко）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d464",
      "text": "\t[カール・レオンハルト]（K. Leonhard）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe1c4000000000078d465",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872133,
      "updated": 1772872133
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49ecb00000000009ec619",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396236,
      "updated": 1772872141
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a02700000000009ec62e",
      "text": "\t> 筆者から付け加えると、人間のタイプは精神的なものだけでなく、身体的な疾患の傾向も左右します。",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396584,
      "updated": 1772396595
    },
    {
      "id": "69a49f7b00000000009ec626",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396411,
      "updated": 1772874578
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe8b3000000000078d50d",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873908,
      "updated": 1772873912
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd513000000000078d3bf",
      "text": "16の[情報代謝タイプ]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868884,
      "updated": 1772869330
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd52d000000000078d3c0",
      "text": "\t主体と客体との情報信号の[送受信チャネル]の型の違い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868910,
      "updated": 1772874998
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd58a000000000078d3c5",
      "text": "\tIEへの焦点の合わせやすさ、識別のしやすさ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772869003,
      "updated": 1772869307
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe8bc000000000078d50f",
      "text": "\t送受信感度の低い情報信号の取り扱いには不安が伴う（見えない敵と戦うようなもの）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772873917,
      "updated": 1772873923
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd75e000000000078d3cf",
      "text": "\t興味と能力分野の差異",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772869470,
      "updated": 1772869470
    },
    {
      "id": "69abecbe000000000078d57a",
      "text": " \t[\" [異なるタイプの人]々は、同じ状況に出会った場合でも、全く異なることを想起し、全く異なる言葉で語る]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874943,
      "updated": 1772874963
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd554000000000078d3c1",
      "text": " \t対応付けられる心理的特性は、[\" 嗜好、能力、関心事項、活動形態、目標設定と行動の動機、他者との関係、美的嗜好、性的嗜好][c. https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=%E3%80%81%E4%BA%BA%E3%81%AE%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%E3%81%AE%E5%A4%9A%E3%81%8F%E3%82%92%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%97%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99%EF%BC%9A%E5%97%9C%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%81%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%81%E9%96%A2%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85%E3%80%81%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%BD%A2%E6%85%8B%E3%80%81%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%A8%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E3%81%AE%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%81%E4%BB%96%E8%80%85%E3%81%A8%E3%81%AE%E9%96%A2%E4%BF%82%E3%80%81%E7%BE%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%97%9C%E5%A5%BD%E3%80%81%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E5%97%9C%E5%A5%BD]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868949,
      "updated": 1772872178
    },
    {
      "id": "69abdfeb000000000078d41c",
      "text": "\t[\" どのような言葉で思考し、どのような表情、ジェスチャー、抑揚でその思考を表出するかが異なっている][cite https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=%E3%81%A9%E3%81%AE%E3%82%88%E3%81%86%E3%81%AA%E8%A8%80%E8%91%89%E3%81%A7%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E3%81%97%E3%80%81%E3%81%A9%E3%81%AE%E3%82%88%E3%81%86%E3%81%AA%E8%A1%A8%E6%83%85%E3%80%81%E3%82%B8%E3%82%A7%E3%82%B9%E3%83%81%E3%83%A3%E3%83%BC%E3%80%81%E6%8A%91%E6%8F%9A%E3%81%A7%E3%81%9D%E3%81%AE%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83%E3%82%92%E8%A1%A8%E5%87%BA%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%81%8B%E3%81%8C%E7%95%B0%E3%81%AA%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%81%84%E3%82%8B%E3%81%8B%E3%82%89]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772871660,
      "updated": 1772871660
    },
    {
      "id": "69abdfeb000000000078d41d",
      "text": "\t[\" 一人の人が他の人を傷つける場合、行動そのものよりも、その行動をどのように説明し、どの動機からその行動をとったと推測するか][cite https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%BA%E3%81%AE%E4%BA%BA%E3%81%8C%E4%BB%96%E3%81%AE%E4%BA%BA%E3%82%92%E5%82%B7%E3%81%A4%E3%81%91%E3%82%8B%E5%A0%B4%E5%90%88%E3%80%81%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E3%81%9D%E3%81%AE%E3%82%82%E3%81%AE%E3%82%88%E3%82%8A%E3%82%82%E3%80%81%E3%81%9D%E3%81%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E3%82%92%E3%81%A9%E3%81%AE%E3%82%88%E3%81%86%E3%81%AB%E8%AA%AC%E6%98%8E%E3%81%97%E3%80%81%E3%81%A9%E3%81%AE%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F%E3%81%8B%E3%82%89%E3%81%9D%E3%81%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E3%82%92%E3%81%A8%E3%81%A3%E3%81%9F%E3%81%A8%E6%8E%A8%E6%B8%AC%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%81%8B%E3%81%AE%E3%81%BB%E3%81%86%E3%81%8C%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E3%81%A7%E3%81%99%E3%80%82]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772871660,
      "updated": 1772871660
    },
    {
      "id": "69abdfeb000000000078d41e",
      "text": "\t[\" 別のある人から見て、その行動はどのような動機から生じた行動だと推測されたのか][c. https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=%E5%88%A5%E3%81%AE%E3%81%82%E3%82%8B%E4%BA%BA%E3%81%8B%E3%82%89%E8%A6%8B%E3%81%A6%E3%80%81%E3%81%9D%E3%81%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E3%81%AF%E3%81%A9%E3%81%AE%E3%82%88%E3%81%86%E3%81%AA%E5%8B%95%E6%A9%9F%E3%81%8B%E3%82%89%E7%94%9F%E3%81%98%E3%81%9F%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E3%81%A0%E3%81%A8%E6%8E%A8%E6%B8%AC%E3%81%95%E3%82%8C%E3%81%9F%E3%81%AE%E3%81%8B]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772871660,
      "updated": 1772871660
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd726000000000078d3cd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772869415,
      "updated": 1772869415
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd557000000000078d3c3",
      "text": "[情報要素] (Information element, IE)",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868952,
      "updated": 1772874969
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd55a000000000078d3c4",
      "text": "\t客体の特定の構成要素、特定の側面（アスペクト）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868955,
      "updated": 1772868997
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd556000000000078d3c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868951,
      "updated": 1772868951
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe458000000000078d47d",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872793,
      "updated": 1772872797
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd5fc000000000078d3c7",
      "text": "[** 人間の相対性と心理的補完]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772869117,
      "updated": 1772872544
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe36a000000000078d475",
      "text": "https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=Augusta）を参照。-,心理的補完が人にもたらすもの,-外向と内向",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872555,
      "updated": 1772872555
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd69a000000000078d3cb",
      "text": "\t〈[情報代謝の阻害]〉",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772869275,
      "updated": 1772873848
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe25d000000000078d469",
      "text": "\t能動的気質と受動的気質",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872286,
      "updated": 1772872364
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe21b000000000078d467",
      "text": " \t[\" もしも二人ともが同じように自発的な人同士であったり、同じように非自発的な人同士であれば、友情は簡単に終わってしまう][c. https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=%E3%82%82%E3%81%97%E3%82%82%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA%E3%81%A8%E3%82%82%E3%81%8C%E5%90%8C%E3%81%98%E3%82%88%E3%81%86%E3%81%AB%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BA%E7%9A%84%E3%81%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E5%A3%AB%E3%81%A7%E3%81%82%E3%81%A3%E3%81%9F%E3%82%8A%E3%80%81%E5%90%8C%E3%81%98%E3%82%88%E3%81%86%E3%81%AB%E9%9D%9E%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BA%E7%9A%84%E3%81%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E5%A3%AB%E3%81%A7%E3%81%82%E3%82%8C%E3%81%B0%E3%80%81%E5%8F%8B%E6%83%85%E3%81%AF%E7%B0%A1%E5%8D%98%E3%81%AB%E7%B5%82%E3%82%8F%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%81%97%E3%81%BE%E3%81%86]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872220,
      "updated": 1772872325
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe247000000000078d468",
      "text": "\tIEの送受信チャネルの分解能の違い",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872264,
      "updated": 1772872395
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe280000000000078d46a",
      "text": "\t\t[\" あるタイプが愛と呼ぶものは、【…】別のあるタイプにとって、それは愛の欠如の証拠にしか見えないかもしれません][c. https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=%E3%81%82%E3%82%8B%E3%82%BF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%97%E3%81%8C%E6%84%9B%E3%81%A8%E5%91%BC%E3%81%B6%E3%82%82%E3%81%AE%E3%81%AF%E3%80%81%E3%81%82%E3%82%8B%E3%82%BF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%97%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A8%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%81%AF%E3%81%BE%E3%81%95%E3%81%AB%E6%84%9B%E3%81%A7%E3%81%82%E3%82%8A%E3%80%81%E6%95%AC%E6%84%8F%E3%82%92%E6%84%9F%E3%81%98%E3%81%95%E3%81%9B%E3%82%89%E3%82%8C%E3%82%8B%E3%82%82%E3%81%AE%E3%81%A7%E3%81%82%E3%82%8B%E3%81%8B%E3%82%82%E3%81%97%E3%82%8C%E3%81%BE%E3%81%9B%E3%82%93%E3%81%8C%E3%80%81%E5%88%A5%E3%81%AE%E3%81%82%E3%82%8B%E3%82%BF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%97%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A8%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A6%E3%80%81%E3%81%9D%E3%82%8C%E3%81%AF%E6%84%9B%E3%81%AE%E6%AC%A0%E5%A6%82%E3%81%AE%E8%A8%BC%E6%8B%A0%E3%81%AB%E3%81%97%E3%81%8B%E8%A6%8B%E3%81%88%E3%81%AA%E3%81%84%E3%81%8B%E3%82%82%E3%81%97%E3%82%8C%E3%81%BE%E3%81%9B%E3%82%93]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872320,
      "updated": 1772872320
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe331000000000078d471",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872498,
      "updated": 1772872498
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe3ce000000000078d47c",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872656,
      "updated": 1772872657
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe338000000000078d472",
      "text": "[** 二分法]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872505,
      "updated": 1772872513
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe323000000000078d46e",
      "text": "[* [静的と動的]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872484,
      "updated": 1772873853
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe323000000000078d46f",
      "text": "https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/01/dual-by-aushra-dichotomy05.html",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872484,
      "updated": 1772872521
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe350000000000078d474",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872529,
      "updated": 1772872529
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe32b000000000078d470",
      "text": "[* [質問と宣言]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872492,
      "updated": 1772873856
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe001000000000078d41f",
      "text": "https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/01/dual-by-aushra-dichotomy06.html",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772871682,
      "updated": 1772872528
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe34e000000000078d473",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872527,
      "updated": 1772872527
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe395000000000078d47a",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872598,
      "updated": 1772872615
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd505000000000078d3bd",
      "text": "[** [ユング二分法]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868870,
      "updated": 1772874219
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe3aa000000000078d47b",
      "text": "\t[[ユングの[『タイプ論』]の概念を理論に組み込んでいるが、あくまで別物]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772872619,
      "updated": 1772874231
    },
    {
      "id": "69abeb5d000000000078d578",
      "text": "\t\t理論の根幹が異なっているため、ユングの用語が情報代謝理論の要素に完全に対応付けられることはない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874590,
      "updated": 1772874677
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe018000000000078d424",
      "text": "\t人の性格をその人の最も顕著な1つまたは2つの機能によって説明付ける",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772871705,
      "updated": 1772871705
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd6eb000000000078d3cc",
      "text": "\t[\" 子供の一方の特性が急速に発展すると、それと対になるもう一方の特性の発展が遅れます][c. https://casual-typology.blogspot.com/2024/03/socionics-dual-nature-of-man.html#:~:text=%E5%AD%90%E4%BE%9B%E3%81%AE%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E3%81%AE%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%E3%81%8C%E6%80%A5%E9%80%9F%E3%81%AB%E7%99%BA%E5%B1%95%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%81%A8%E3%80%81%E3%81%9D%E3%82%8C%E3%81%A8%E5%AF%BE%E3%81%AB%E3%81%AA%E3%82%8B%E3%82%82%E3%81%86%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E3%81%AE%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7%E3%81%AE%E7%99%BA%E5%B1%95%E3%81%8C%E9%81%85%E3%82%8C%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772869357,
      "updated": 1772869366
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a07d00000000009ec631",
      "text": " \tユングの用語のうち、〈思考〉(Thinking) と〈感情〉(Feeling) は誤解を招く表現である",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396670,
      "updated": 1772874266
    },
    {
      "id": "69abea19000000000078d53c",
      "text": " \tソシオニクスではこの側面を〈論理〉〈倫理〉と呼称する",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874266,
      "updated": 1772874285
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a14200000000009ec636",
      "text": " \t\tここでオーシュラは[\" 思考タイプは客観的なことについて、後者は自分たちを取り巻く世界について、主観的に思考している]としている",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396867,
      "updated": 1772871714
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a18b00000000009ec637",
      "text": " \t\tNote: 元々のユングの二分法において〈客観的〉〈主観的〉と対応させられていたのは、〈外向的〉と〈内向的〉の方である",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396940,
      "updated": 1772874306
    },
    {
      "id": "69abea3b000000000078d53d",
      "text": " \t\tNote: このオーシュラの対応付けには異論もある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874300,
      "updated": 1772874337
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4a0b200000000009ec635",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772396723,
      "updated": 1772873944
    },
    {
      "id": "69abe922000000000078d53b",
      "text": "[hr.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772874019,
      "updated": 1772874026
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd4cd000000000078d3b8",
      "text": "[* [外向性]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868814,
      "updated": 1772873869
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd4ce000000000078d3b9",
      "text": "\t[分裂病質]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868815,
      "updated": 1772873879
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd4cf000000000078d3ba",
      "text": "[* [内向性]]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868816,
      "updated": 1772873871
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd4e0000000000078d3bb",
      "text": "\t[循環気質]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868833,
      "updated": 1772873874
    },
    {
      "id": "69abd4c7000000000078d3b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772868808,
      "updated": 1772872865
    },
